# Frontend public configuration (API base URL + OIDC settings) is loaded at
# RUNTIME from /config.json — it is no longer set via build-time VITE_* env vars.
#
#   - Local dev:   edit apps/frontend/public/config.json (defaults already target
#                  the backend proxy + the dockerized Keycloak realm from GP-6).
#   - Production:  mount a config.json over /usr/share/nginx/html/config.json
#                  (see frontend-config.json.example at the repo root).
#
# There are currently no build-time VITE_* variables to set, so this .env is
# empty. See apps/frontend/src/config.ts for the config shape and defaults.
